OL,3,CThe 154th Open at Royal Birkdale:
OL,4,CEverything you need to know
OL,6,FThe best golfers in the world are
OL,7,Fdescending on Southport for the 154th
OL,8,FOpen Championship at Royal Birkdale
OL,9,Ffor the four-day tournament.
OL,11,FStaged at the historic Merseyside
OL,12,Fvenue for the 11th time, this year's
OL,13,FOpen promises a fiercely competitive
OL,14,Ffield, with a course layout that has
OL,15,Fundergone some major updates since the
OL,16,FClaret Jug was last lifted there.
OL,18,FWhether you are heading to the green
OL,19,For watching from your living room,
OL,20,Fhere is everything you need to know:
