OL,3,CThe 154th Open at Royal Birkdale:
OL,4,CEverything you need to know
OL,6,FThe Schedule: Key Dates & Times
OL,8,FThe Open takes place across a full
OL,9,Fweek, with practice sessions taking
OL,10,Fplace at the beginning and finishing
OL,11,Foff with four intense rounds of
OL,12,Fchampionship golf.
OL,14,FWhat's new at Royal Birkdale?
OL,16,FFirst hosting The Open in 1954, Royal
OL,17,FBirkdale is widely regarded as one of
OL,18,Fthe fairest yet most "unforgiving"
OL,19,Flinks courses in the world because of
OL,20,Fits terrain of natural sand dunes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
