OL,3,CThe 154th Open at Royal Birkdale:
OL,4,CEverything you need to know
OL,6,FThe course offers spectators
OL,7,Fincredible views but leaves players
OL,8,Fzero room for error if the coastal
OL,9,Fwinds pick up.
OL,11,FHowever, competitors will face a whole
OL,12,Fnew challenge this year as significant
OL,13,Fcourse updates have taken place across
OL,14,Fthe course.
OL,16,FAccording to organisers, five changes
OL,17,Fwill test world class field at The
OL,18,F154th Open, including:
OL,20,FWho to watch
