OL,3,CThe 154th Open at Royal Birkdale:
OL,4,CEverything you need to know
OL,6,FThe last time The Open was held at
OL,7,FBirkdale was in 2017, with US golfer
OL,8,FJordan Spieth winning a final-round
OL,9,Fduel. He will be looking to recapture
OL,10,Fthat day when he competes in this
OL,11,Fyear's tournament.
OL,13,F2024 Champion Xander Schauffele, from
OL,14,Fthe US, will also look to pick up the
OL,15,Ftrophy, alongside Rory McIlroy, Ludvig
OL,16,FAberg, and Tommy Fleetwood, who will
OL,17,Flikely have the loudest backing from
OL,18,Fhis hometown crowds.
OL,20,FHow do I get there?
