OL,3,CThe 154th Open at Royal Birkdale:
OL,4,CEverything you need to know
OL,6,FTaking the train is the primary
OL,7,Frecommended method of travel for the
OL,8,Ftournament.
OL,10,FDriving and Park & Ride
OL,12,FLocal Buses
OL,14,FCycling or walking
OL,16,FCan I bring a bag?
OL,18,FOrganisers ask spectators to keep in
OL,19,Fmind that Royal Birkdale has a strict
OL,20,Fbag policy.
