OL,3,CThe 154th Open at Royal Birkdale:
OL,4,CEverything you need to know
OL,6,FLarge suitcases and travel bags are
OL,7,Fnot permitted, so you will need to
OL,8,Futilise local luggage storage options
OL,9,Fif you are coming straight from the
OL,10,Fairport or a long-distance train.
OL,12,FHow to follow the action
OL,14,FIf you missed out on the ticket
OL,15,Fballot, you can enjoy the open through
OL,16,Fthe official Open App.
